window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>One way or another, the end comes for all, gods and men alike.</b></p> <p>Enemies in both the mortal realm and amongst the gods are coming out. Rob's family has come together, though, and will stand together against all challengers.</p> <p>Now, it's time to show them the final law. Even gods must face the consequences of their actions—and who better to show them than the Sheriff?</p>"; 
